descriptionHtml:
This is a quick re-texture i made for the nightingale armour for my liking and im sure for other peoples liking if you wish to play as a elf/ranger with green equipment. 

credit goes Warhammer online concept art for the cape design

I will bring updates hopefully and highlight areas that need work for example i may add gold trimming onto the armour, im not sure yet.

to install, put the folder \"textures\" into
C\\program files\\steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\data
author: tomolyons
